data.name: CONVENTIONAL HYPODERMIC 2-PARTS SYRINGES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Luer Slip Tips
- With and Without Needle
- Customizable graduation including logo
- Some Sizes with Centric and Excentric luer Tips

## PERFORMANCE
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency Barrel
- Smooth sliding
- Smooth Surface
